               <div class="itemInnerContent">
                <p>
                 Established in 1991, Salt Creek Office Furniture has been owned and operated by the Cameron Family. When you visit one of our location in Scottsdale or Tempe, you will work with a family member and be treated as a welcomed guest in our store.

             <div class="item itemPreview">
              <div class="itemContent">
               <h2 class="contentTitle">
                Wholesale Furniture in a Retail Store!
               </h2>
               <div class="itemInnerContent">
                <p>
                 Salt Creek Office Furniture offers all
                 <a href="https://saltcreekofficefurniture.com/home-office-furniture">
                  home office furniture
                 </a>
                 products at a deep discount from suggested retail prices EVERYDAY. We do not run  gimmicky sales programs. Our business concept is to offer discounts   from suggested retail prices from 30%–60%, depending on the product   line, to our customers year round.
                </p>
               </div>

            <div class="blockText">
             <div class="blockInnerContent">
              <div class="txtCols2">
               <p>
                We offer a “
                <strong>
                 ZERO pressure
                </strong>
                ” retail environment as we  have created a shopping experience that reflects our own desires as  consumers, to be let alone and allowed to peruse the selections offered  and then be assisted when help is required.
               </p>
               <p>
                Quality home office furniture in Scottsdale or Phoenix can be hard to find, but when you are ready for assistance, we can offer you many  services, including space planning services, office workstation  furniture, furniture selection ideas, assistance with layouts for your  home office or for an office of 100 people and more!
               </p>
               <p>
                We are happy you came to our site today; we hope to see you soon and assist you how we may, in either of our locations in Scottsdale and Tempe.
               </p>
               <p>
                <strong>
                 Ed Cameron, Managing Partner (and Dad).
                </strong>
               </p>
